Use Visualforce to Embed CRM Analytics Dashboards in Experience Cloud Sites

Required editions: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited Editions, Developer Edition.
User permissions needed:
  Create and Set Up Experiences
  Analytics Growth permission set license with Manage Analytics permission
  Analytics for Communities permission set license with View Analytics on Communities pages permission

To embed a dashboard, see Add a CRM Analytics Dashboard to a Visualforce Page.
title: Embedding CRM Analytics Dashboards in Experience Cloud Sites
